4
00:01:47,350 --> 00:01:47,950
Xiangyi.

5
00:01:49,780 --> 00:01:50,789
Do you think that

6
00:01:52,539 --> 00:01:54,070
what you say is always right,

7
00:01:54,070 --> 00:01:55,070
always the truth,

8
00:01:55,259 --> 00:01:57,520
and Sigu Sect can't survive without you?

9
00:01:58,100 --> 00:01:58,560
Yes.

10
00:02:03,840 --> 00:02:05,640
It has been proven over the years

11
00:02:06,650 --> 00:02:07,980
that all these are true.

12
00:02:08,990 --> 00:02:10,520
Sigu Sect will run normally

13
00:02:11,380 --> 00:02:12,840
regardless of who leaves.

14
00:02:14,220 --> 00:02:15,650
