15
00:02:16,919 --> 00:02:17,850
it'll collapse.

16
00:02:19,030 --> 00:02:19,540
Fine.

17
00:02:25,530 --> 00:02:26,860
You've finally said it.

18
00:02:27,980 --> 00:02:30,180
We grew up together since we were young.

19
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:31,579
When there was food, I couldn't bear to eat them,

20
00:02:31,579 --> 00:02:32,850
and I gave all of them to you.

21
00:02:32,850 --> 00:02:34,980
I also gave you the best sword I forged.

22
00:02:36,010 --> 00:02:36,980
Deep down,

23
00:02:37,980 --> 00:02:39,260
I value you

24
00:02:39,260 --> 00:02:40,260
more than myself.

25
00:02:45,020 --> 00:02:46,079
But what about you?

26
00:02:52,600 --> 00:02:54,329
Since Sigu Sect only needs you,

27
00:02:56,920 --> 00:02:57,650
I quit.

28
