♫I asked myself tens of thousands of times♫

33
00:03:22,320 --> 00:03:24,190
♫Which moment♫

34
00:03:25,210 --> 00:03:27,840
♫I'd never forget♫

35
00:03:26,900 --> 00:03:27,720
Sect Leader.

36
00:03:28,630 --> 00:03:30,870
♫The martial world♫

37
00:03:30,890 --> 00:03:32,490
♫Is so big and fascinating♫

38
00:03:32,510 --> 00:03:34,610
♫We're all wanderers in it♫

39
