♫Let's drink away all our sorrows♫

44
00:03:48,180 --> 00:03:48,760
Senior.

45
00:03:48,350 --> 00:03:53,110
♫Life is like a dream♫

46
00:03:52,579 --> 00:03:53,180
Senior.

47
00:03:53,130 --> 00:03:57,180
♫Our story ends here♫

48
00:04:04,700 --> 00:04:05,240
Senior.

49
00:04:07,320 --> 00:04:07,990
Senior!

50
00:04:18,700 --> 00:04:19,430
Sect Leader.

51
00:04:19,640 --> 00:04:21,580
We were ambushed by the Jinyuan Alliance.

52
00:04:21,580 --> 00:04:23,990
Senior's dead body was snatched too.

53
00:04:25,070 --> 00:04:28,000
It was a trick of luring the tiger out of the mountain.

54
00:04:28,610 --> 00:04:30,270
Sigu Sect, listen to my order.

55
00:04:30,860 --> 00:04:31,990
From today onwards,

56
00:04:33,050 --> 00:04:34,910
we'll fight the Jinyuan Alliance

57
00:04:35,610 --> 00:04:36,810
till death do us part.

58
00:04:43,670 --> 00:04:44,750
Li Lianhua.

59
00:04:47,020 --> 00:04:48,350
Why are you spacing out?

60
00:04:49,060 --> 00:04:50,650
Since I exposed your nonsense,

61
00:04:50,650 --> 00:04:52,780
you don't know how to quibble anymore, do you?

62
00:04:52,780 --> 00:04:54,510
I can't hide anything from you.

63
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:55,310
Of course.

64
00:04:55,700 --> 00:04:56,909
They are very close.

65
00:04:57,280 --> 00:04:58,690
I'll spare your life today.

66
00:04:58,690 --> 00:05:00,290
Don't spread rumours again.

67
00:05:02,530 --> 00:05:03,390
It's time to go.

68
00:05:12,370 --> 00:05:13,700
Fei knows my uncle.

69
00:05:14,340 --> 00:05:15,830
He must know Li Xiangyi.

70
00:05:18,300 --> 00:05:20,300
Fei is not familiar with Li Xiangyi.

71
00:05:20,420 --> 00:05:21,820
You don't have to ask him.

72
00:05:22,110 --> 00:05:23,370
I don't care about others,

73
00:05:23,370 --> 00:05:24,970
but I must find out about Fei.

74
00:05:25,510 --> 00:05:26,530
He is so bad at martial arts

75
00:05:26,530 --> 00:05:27,460
but so arrogant.

76
00:05:27,540 --> 00:05:29,270
There must be something fishy.

77
00:05:29,380 --> 00:05:29,840
Come on.

78
00:05:30,130 --> 00:05:31,410
Let's go to Baichuan Court together.

79
00:05:31,410 --> 00:05:33,340
Why are we going to Baichuan Court?

80
00:05:34,270 --> 00:05:35,380
Counting the murder cases in Cailian Manor,

81
00:05:35,380 --> 00:05:37,140
I've already solved three major cases.

82
00:05:37,140 --> 00:05:38,340
It's time to go to Baichuan Court

83
00:05:38,340 --> 00:05:39,810
for the real detective badge.

84
00:05:39,810 --> 00:05:41,730
If so, you will have Baichuan Court as your partner

85
00:05:41,730 --> 00:05:43,330
when you become a detective.

86
00:05:43,970 --> 00:05:45,030
Congratulations.

87
00:05:45,970 --> 00:05:46,830
Same to you.

88
00:05:47,320 --> 00:05:48,720
You used to be my partner,

89
00:05:48,880 --> 00:05:50,560
and you'll also be the only one in the future.

90
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:51,420
How about this?

91
00:05:51,430 --> 00:05:52,960
We'll imitate the Sigu Sect

92
00:05:53,140 --> 00:05:54,600
to solve mysterious cases

93
00:05:54,780 --> 00:05:56,140
and rectify the martial arts world.

94
00:05:56,140 --> 00:05:56,670
Let's go.

95
00:06:02,220 --> 00:06:03,220
So much money?

96
00:06:03,900 --> 00:06:04,560
Li Lianhua,

97
00:06:04,980 --> 00:06:05,659
did you strike gold

98
00:06:05,659 --> 00:06:06,460
or get a fever?

99
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:08,000
You're leaving soon.

100
00:06:08,220 --> 00:06:09,340
If you don't prepare well,

101
00:06:09,340 --> 00:06:11,100
you may starve to death on the way.

102
00:06:11,100 --> 00:06:12,760
Take it to buy some solid food.

103
00:06:13,730 --> 00:06:14,360
No need?

104
00:06:14,540 --> 00:06:16,740
Fine, if you don't need it, I can just...

105
00:06:16,970 --> 00:06:20,230
It's a rare opportunity for misers like you to be generous.

106
00:06:20,410 --> 00:06:22,340
I'll go buy food in town right away.

107
00:06:23,890 --> 00:06:24,490
By the way,

108
00:06:24,910 --> 00:06:25,910
keep an eye on Fei.

109
00:06:26,050 --> 00:06:28,180
I'll investigate him when I come back.

110
00:06:41,020 --> 00:06:42,950
I bought a lot of fresh vegetables.

111
00:06:48,630 --> 00:06:49,400
Li Lianhua!

112
00:06:55,170 --> 00:06:56,200
[To Mr. Worried]

113
00:07:01,340 --> 00:07:02,700
"Fei and I have personal affairs to attend to.

114
00:07:02,700 --> 00:07:03,620
We have to take our leave.

115
00:07:03,620 --> 00:07:05,200
So I'm writing this letter to inform you.

116
00:07:05,200 --> 00:07:07,530
I'm not leaving without saying goodbye."

117
00:07:07,900 --> 00:07:09,030
You cunning old fox.

118
00:07:10,140 --> 00:07:11,340
"I'm not an old fox,

119
00:07:11,370 --> 00:07:12,540
and I'm not cunning at all.

120
00:07:12,540 --> 00:07:13,780
This letter is to warn my friend

121
00:07:13,780 --> 00:07:14,900
to stop sulking

122
00:07:14,900 --> 00:07:16,340
and leave this place as soon as possible.

123
00:07:16,340 --> 00:07:17,780
Otherwise, things will change."

124
00:07:17,780 --> 00:07:19,440
There's no way I will buy that.

125
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:21,480
"You can surely buy that.

126
00:07:21,780 --> 00:07:23,980
Please check it out behind the rock.

127
00:07:26,140 --> 00:07:27,140
I've sent out a smoke signal.

128
00:07:27,140 --> 00:07:28,860
Your aunt is coming to catch you.

129
00:07:28,860 --> 00:07:30,620
Leave now."

130
00:07:32,630 --> 00:07:33,290
Li Lianhua,

131
00:07:33,570 --> 00:07:34,450
I hate you!

132
00:07:44,020 --> 00:07:44,550
Hurry up.

133
00:07:59,520 --> 00:08:00,250
Director Di,

134
00:08:00,659 --> 00:08:03,460
you've emptied all the pharmacies nearby, right?

135
00:08:03,780 --> 00:08:04,510
Let's begin.

136
00:08:08,890 --> 00:08:10,490
To practice this technique,

137
00:08:10,780 --> 00:08:12,020
you have to insert silver needles at certain anatomical points

138
00:08:12,020 --> 00:08:15,200
and take herbal medicine to get the poison out of your body.

139
00:08:15,200 --> 00:08:15,960
Director Di,

140
00:08:16,260 --> 00:08:17,410
please meditate and circulate your qi.

141
00:08:17,410 --> 00:08:18,720
I'll perform the acupuncture.

142
00:08:18,720 --> 00:08:19,560
Li Xiangyi,

143
00:08:20,020 --> 00:08:23,350
don't play tricks with me when it's related to martial arts.

144
00:08:23,880 --> 00:08:25,080
It's been ten years since we saw each other,

145
00:08:25,080 --> 00:08:26,940
and you've become more vigilant.

146
00:08:27,330 --> 00:08:28,170
Don't worry.

147
00:08:28,390 --> 00:08:29,720
I won't play any tricks.

148
00:08:30,770 --> 00:08:31,700
It would be best.

149
00:08:53,980 --> 00:08:54,940
I've told you

150
00:08:55,420 --> 00:08:56,340
the mantra.

151
00:08:57,170 --> 00:08:59,480
Circulate your inner breath for 49 days,

152
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:02,840
and the poison of the Xiuluo Grass will be detoxified.

153
00:09:03,010 --> 00:09:05,400
Remember, it's 49 days.

154
00:09:06,290 --> 00:09:07,490
Don't miss even a bit.

155
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:17,880
Do you hear me?

156
00:09:18,420 --> 00:09:19,150
Director Di.

157
00:09:20,060 --> 00:09:20,860
Do you hear me?

158
00:09:21,180 --> 00:09:21,910
Director Di.

159
00:09:35,460 --> 00:09:36,520
When should I leave

160
00:09:36,580 --> 00:09:37,810
if not now?

161
00:09:42,340 --> 00:09:43,260
My Lord ordered that

162
00:09:43,260 --> 00:09:45,100
I must make Sect Leader Li stay.

163
00:09:46,530 --> 00:09:48,260
Your Lord just said I can leave.

164
00:09:54,420 --> 00:09:54,930
Oh no.

165
00:09:55,740 --> 00:09:57,140
The poisonous grass has backfired on Your Lord.

166
00:09:57,140 --> 00:09:58,600
Go quickly and have a look.

167
00:10:15,250 --> 00:10:17,180
You have recovered just like that?

168
00:10:17,220 --> 00:10:20,020
I didn't realize how quickly 49 days went by.

169
00:10:20,650 --> 00:10:21,780
Where are you going?

170
00:10:22,120 --> 00:10:23,050
We're even now.

171
00:10:23,890 --> 00:10:25,120
So I'm leaving.

172
00:10:25,560 --> 00:10:27,340
I promised not to expose your identity.

173
00:10:27,340 --> 00:10:29,350
But do you think you can retire from the martial arts world

174
00:10:29,350 --> 00:10:30,480
and die like a loser?

175
00:10:31,700 --> 00:10:32,700
You're too naive.

176
00:10:33,420 --> 00:10:34,230
Director Di,

177
00:10:35,460 --> 00:10:36,720
why bother forcing me?

178
00:10:37,300 --> 00:10:38,900
All I want is for you to live on

179
00:10:39,420 --> 00:10:40,750
and fight with me again.

180
00:10:50,760 --> 00:10:53,230
Greetings, My Lord.

181
00:10:53,780 --> 00:10:54,710
Medicine Demon.

182
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:58,320
I want him to regain his inner power.

183
00:11:08,030 --> 00:11:08,670
My Lord,

184
00:11:09,220 --> 00:11:10,980
he is severely injured.

185
00:11:11,810 --> 00:11:13,270
It's not easy to deal with.

186
00:11:13,350 --> 00:11:14,150
Is it not easy,

187
00:11:14,680 --> 00:11:16,480
or are you not competent enough?

188
00:11:16,970 --> 00:11:17,860
No, no, no.

189
00:11:19,140 --> 00:11:21,110
My Lord, if you want him to recover,

190
00:11:21,430 --> 00:11:23,330
I'll try my best.

191
00:11:23,760 --> 00:11:25,990
My Lord, please come with me.

192
00:11:28,770 --> 00:11:29,300
Let's go.

193
00:11:30,450 --> 00:11:30,980
Move.

194
00:11:41,980 --> 00:11:42,620
My Lord,

195
00:11:43,300 --> 00:11:44,680
Hundreds Herbs Syrup

196
00:11:44,780 --> 00:11:47,380
is a treasure I have decocted

197
00:11:47,410 --> 00:11:49,410
with hundreds of exotic herbs for over ten years.

198
00:11:49,410 --> 00:11:51,860
Normally, a cup of it works.

199
00:11:52,260 --> 00:11:53,500
But if you drink too much,

200
00:11:53,500 --> 00:11:56,760
your meridians will overreact and cause unbearable pain.

201
00:11:57,420 --> 00:11:58,080
Drink that.

202
00:12:03,060 --> 00:12:03,680
Please.

203
00:12:17,550 --> 00:12:18,870
With his injury,

204
00:12:19,330 --> 00:12:21,370
one cup may not work.

205
00:12:21,460 --> 00:12:22,070
Go on.

206
00:12:45,380 --> 00:12:46,540
It's so bitter.

207
00:12:48,930 --> 00:12:49,870
Well...

208
00:12:51,180 --> 00:12:51,830
Feed him.

209
00:12:52,700 --> 00:12:53,430
Yes, My Lord.

210
00:12:59,730 --> 00:13:00,310
Please.

211
00:13:02,270 --> 00:13:02,910
Thank you.

212
00:13:02,980 --> 00:13:03,980
I'll do it myself.

213
00:13:19,970 --> 00:13:20,610
My Lord,

214
00:13:21,010 --> 00:13:22,870
this guy's qi has been disrupted.

215
00:13:22,900 --> 00:13:24,230
His inner power is weak.

216
00:13:24,300 --> 00:13:24,760
Well...

217
00:13:24,930 --> 00:13:27,300
Even three cups are of no avail.

218
00:13:31,830 --> 00:13:33,160
His inner power is weak?

219
00:13:39,890 --> 00:13:42,090
I'll insert my inner power into his body

220
00:13:42,930 --> 00:13:44,590
to stimulate the drug effect.

221
00:14:08,850 --> 00:14:09,460
My Lord.

222
00:14:10,060 --> 00:14:11,810
He will die if you do so.

223
00:14:29,980 --> 00:14:31,440
I told you it's incurable.

224
00:14:32,350 --> 00:14:34,010
It's such a waste of resources

225
00:14:34,060 --> 00:14:36,920
for Director Di to get me all these treasures.

226
00:14:38,570 --> 00:14:39,770
Think of another way.

227
00:14:42,500 --> 00:14:43,340
Think of a way.

228
00:14:45,640 --> 00:14:49,950
We can give it a shot at the Spiritual Snake Cave.

229
00:14:51,910 --> 00:14:53,360
Spiritual Snake Cave?

230
00:15:04,820 --> 00:15:05,460
My Lord,

231
00:15:05,950 --> 00:15:07,580
these spiritual flood dragons in the Eastern Sea

232
00:15:07,580 --> 00:15:10,580
have been fed with spiritual medicine for many years.

233
00:15:10,780 --> 00:15:12,930
They like to suck people's qi and feed them again.

234
00:15:12,930 --> 00:15:15,330
Now that this guy's qi is disrupted.

235
00:15:15,490 --> 00:15:18,310
Let's have an exchange transfusion for him.

236
00:15:18,610 --> 00:15:20,610
It might work.

237
00:15:21,770 --> 00:15:22,650
Let's try then.

238
00:15:50,750 --> 00:15:52,780
B-Bicha Poison?

239
00:15:53,280 --> 00:15:53,830
My Lord.

240
00:15:54,540 --> 00:15:56,800
He was poisoned by Bicha Poison.

241
00:16:02,340 --> 00:16:02,920
Useless!

242
00:16:04,580 --> 00:16:06,040
My Lord, please calm down.

243
00:16:06,230 --> 00:16:08,430
If you want him to regain his inner power,

244
00:16:08,430 --> 00:16:09,270
and fight him,

245
00:16:09,390 --> 00:16:10,710
there's another way.

246
00:16:10,740 --> 00:16:11,140
Say it.

247
00:16:11,770 --> 00:16:13,020
Wangchuan Flower.

248
00:16:14,530 --> 00:16:15,590
Wangchuan Flower?

249
00:16:16,860 --> 00:16:18,210
It has the supreme yang.

250
00:16:18,670 --> 00:16:21,670
It can help me break through the eighth level of the Windy Poplar.

251
00:16:21,670 --> 00:16:23,750
But his inner power is not strong.

252
00:16:23,930 --> 00:16:24,990
How can it cure him?

253
00:16:27,410 --> 00:16:28,400
My Lord,

254
00:16:28,700 --> 00:16:31,540
Wangchuan Flower has two different types, namely Yin and Yang.

255
00:16:31,540 --> 00:16:34,370
The Yang grass is a kind of martial art, same as you.

256
00:16:34,740 --> 00:16:35,770
While the Yin grass

257
00:16:35,770 --> 00:16:37,900
is the most poisonous grass in the world.

258
00:16:37,900 --> 00:16:39,760
Even if a child takes it,

259
00:16:39,950 --> 00:16:42,810
they can gain more than ten years of martial skills.

260
00:16:42,880 --> 00:16:45,260
But it's like the last radiance of the setting sun.

261
00:16:45,260 --> 00:16:46,540
A few days later,

262
00:16:46,780 --> 00:16:48,870
the Yin grass will start to have a strong effect,

263
00:16:48,870 --> 00:16:50,400
and it will get stronger and stronger.

264
00:16:50,400 --> 00:16:52,140
His meridians will break

265
00:16:52,180 --> 00:16:53,550
and his organs will split.

266
00:16:53,550 --> 00:16:56,710
There is no other way to die more terribly

267
00:16:56,740 --> 00:16:58,980
than it in the world.

268
00:16:59,180 --> 00:17:01,110
I don't want him to live a long life.

269
00:17:01,520 --> 00:17:03,820
I just want him to live on until we fight again.

270
00:17:03,820 --> 00:17:04,460
Let's go.

271
00:17:05,700 --> 00:17:07,300
I want the Wangchuan Flower.

272
00:17:07,970 --> 00:17:09,400
Yes, My Lord.

273
00:17:21,020 --> 00:17:22,220
Why are you laughing?

274
00:17:23,220 --> 00:17:23,950
Director Di,

275
00:17:25,420 --> 00:17:26,980
stop wasting your time.

276
00:17:27,859 --> 00:17:29,220
It's all for nothing.

277
00:17:30,220 --> 00:17:32,650
So what if you get the Wangchuan Flower?

278
00:17:33,339 --> 00:17:34,770
You can force me to eat it,

279
00:17:35,560 --> 00:17:37,700
but you can't force me to fight with you.

280
00:17:37,700 --> 00:17:39,540
By then, I'll lie in front of you

281
00:17:39,620 --> 00:17:41,420
and wait for death under the sun,

282
00:17:41,620 --> 00:17:42,750
