00:33:09,240 --> 00:33:10,240
Don't get choked.

563
00:33:33,160 --> 00:33:33,880
I'm not eating.

564
00:33:33,880 --> 00:33:34,340
You eat.

565
00:33:35,100 --> 00:33:36,500
Why are you staring at me?

566
00:33:39,900 --> 00:33:40,740
It's nothing.

567
00:33:41,960 --> 00:33:43,820
Aren't you more like your mother?

568
00:33:46,100 --> 00:33:47,900
What kind of nonsense is that?

569
00:33:48,290 --> 00:33:49,530
Our butler said

570
00:33:49,800 --> 00:33:51,700
I resemble my second aunt the most.

571
00:33:51,700 --> 00:33:52,760
But when I was born,

572
00:33:52,890 --> 00:33:54,690
my second aunt had already died.

573
00:33:59,380 --> 00:34:01,510
You didn't see your uncles many times.

574
00:34:01,940 --> 00:34:03,070
When you were young,

575
00:34:04,040 --> 00:34:05,340
did he dote on you much?

576
00:34:05,900 --> 00:34:08,230
My uncle is the second master of the Sigu Sect.

577
00:34:08,230 --> 00:34:09,440
He was usually very busy.

578
00:34:09,440 --> 00:34:10,900
He didn't have time for me.

579
00:34:11,140 --> 00:34:13,800
Besides, my mother seemed to hate him very much.

580
00:34:14,130 --> 00:34:16,260
She didn't allow me to get close to him.

581
00:34:21,659 --> 00:34:24,260
Why do you suddenly ask about my family matter?

582
00:34:25,659 --> 00:34:26,460
It's nothing.

583
00:34:27,030 --> 00:34:28,280
I was just asking.

584
00:34:28,900 --> 00:34:29,830
Eat your buns.

585
00:34:33,000 --> 00:34:34,060
Then let me ask you.

586
00:34:34,420 --> 00:34:36,150
You have to answer me honestly.

587
00:34:36,540 --> 00:34:38,469
Who is Fei exactly?

588
00:34:38,860 --> 00:34:40,860
Why is he so skilful in martial arts?

589
00:34:42,530 --> 00:34:44,190
Since we are now at this point,

590
00:34:44,199 --> 00:34:46,000
I won't hide it from you anymore.

591
00:34:46,210 --> 00:34:47,290
He's Di Feisheng.

592
00:34:49,340 --> 00:34:51,159
D-Di Feisheng?

593
00:34:51,889 --> 00:34:54,100
The devil of the Jinyuan Alliance, Di Feisheng?

594
00:34:54,100 --> 00:34:54,560
Well...

595
00:34:55,980 --> 00:34:57,260
Do you know my master

596
00:34:57,260 --> 00:34:59,170
is unaccounted for ten years because of him?

597
00:34:59,170 --> 00:35:01,230
How can you hang out with such a devil?

598
00:35:03,180 --> 00:35:04,990
He asked me to promise him to save someone.

599
00:35:04,990 --> 00:35:05,790
Save someone?

600
00:35:06,460 --> 00:35:08,100
You can lie with your medical skills,

601
00:35:08,100 --> 00:35:09,900
but you can't save lives with it.

602
00:35:10,400 --> 00:35:13,400
There are people in this world

603
00:35:14,390 --> 00:35:15,850
who can only be saved by me.

604
00:35:17,050 --> 00:35:17,980
Unfortunately,

605
00:35:19,300 --> 00:35:20,700
I don't want to save them.

606
00:35:20,780 --> 00:35:22,180
So you left me behind

607
00:35:22,910 --> 00:35:25,120
because you were afraid Di Feisheng would deal with me,

608
00:35:25,120 --> 00:35:26,090
but it turned out that you were caught

609
00:35:26,090 --> 00:35:27,740
and got hurt all over your body.

610
00:35:27,740 --> 00:35:28,400
Li Lianhua,

611
00:35:28,610 --> 00:35:29,980
I won't accept your kindness for that.

612
00:35:29,980 --> 00:35:31,850
We agreed that friends should share weal and woe.

613
00:35:31,850 --> 00:35:33,850
Even if the opponent is Di Feisheng.

614
00:35:37,110 --> 00:35:38,040
Young Hero Fang,

615
00:35:38,480 --> 00:35:39,540
I know you're good.

616
00:35:40,010 --> 00:35:41,340
It's my fault this time.

617
00:35:41,710 --> 00:35:42,310
Thank you.

618
00:35:42,770 --> 00:35:44,500
At least you have a conscience.

619
00:35:44,540 --> 00:35:45,140
By the way,

620
00:35:45,340 --> 00:35:46,820
don't promise Di Feisheng

621
00:35:47,160 --> 00:35:48,730
to save the person he mentioned.

622
00:35:48,730 --> 00:35:49,910
The person he wants to save

623
00:35:49,910 --> 00:35:51,710
is definitely not a good person.

624
00:35:53,140 --> 00:35:54,800
He is indeed not a good person.

625
00:35:56,000 --> 00:35:56,960
I won't save him.

626
00:35:57,730 --> 00:35:59,590
It's more important to save you now.

627
00:35:59,590 --> 00:36:00,450
Di Feisheng has inserted Gang Qi

628
00:36:00,450 --> 00:36:02,360
into your body.

629
00:36:03,060 --> 00:36:04,320
It'll be troublesome.

630
00:36:06,180 --> 00:36:06,990
It doesn't matter.

631
00:36:06,990 --> 00:36:08,260
I'm talented.

632
00:36:08,660 --> 00:36:09,960
I felt a little uncomfortable just now.

633
00:36:09,960 --> 00:36:10,560
Look now.

634
00:36:10,850 --> 00:36:11,830
I'm fine.

635
00:36:36,510 --> 00:36:38,380
I don't have much inner power left.

636
00:36:38,380 --> 00:36:41,190
I almost can't deploy my power to suppress the Gang Qi.

637
00:36:41,190 --> 00:36:43,190
But if Gang Qi reaches his temple,

638
00:36:44,020 --> 00:36:45,080
he will surely die.

639
00:36:45,890 --> 00:36:47,020
This is the only way.

640
00:36:53,400 --> 00:36:54,200
You're awake.

641
00:36:59,560 --> 00:37:01,420
Get up and have some warm water.

642
00:37:03,680 --> 00:37:04,880
Why did I faint again?

643
00:37:06,150 --> 00:37:07,290
You've been inserted Gang Qi.

644
00:37:07,290 --> 00:37:08,820
You fainted all of a sudden.

645
00:37:09,770 --> 00:37:11,070
I didn't expect that you are so heavy

646
00:37:11,070 --> 00:37:12,530
that I was exhausted

647
00:37:12,880 --> 00:37:14,880
to carry you back to the Lotus Tower.

648
00:37:18,870 --> 00:37:22,470
Practice the skill set according to the papers I put on the table.

649
00:37:22,780 --> 00:37:24,040
Practice it properly.

650
00:37:34,050 --> 00:37:34,780
What is this?

651
00:37:35,530 --> 00:37:36,230
A draft?

652
00:37:38,100 --> 00:37:38,870
A draft?

653
00:37:39,880 --> 00:37:41,410
This is an ancestral skill.

654
00:37:41,980 --> 00:37:42,710
Previously,

655
00:37:42,790 --> 00:37:44,000
the Gang Qi inside your body

656
00:37:44,000 --> 00:37:45,390
was suppressed by it.

657
00:37:45,990 --> 00:37:46,870
Study hard.

658
00:37:47,140 --> 00:37:48,710
Don't bother me anymore.

659
00:37:50,090 --> 00:37:51,370
It's ancestral?

660
00:37:52,030 --> 00:37:53,480
The ink is not dry yet.

661
00:37:53,930 --> 00:37:55,260
Did you draw it just now?

662
00:37:55,920 --> 00:37:57,450
The ancestral martial arts

663
00:37:57,460 --> 00:37:59,140
must be passed down by word of mouth.

664
00:37:59,140 --> 00:38:00,330
So I drew it for you

665
00:38:00,370 --> 00:38:01,630
to make you understand

666
00:38:01,740 --> 00:38:02,600
and learn well.

667
00:38:02,830 --> 00:38:03,560
Understand?

668
00:38:04,530 --> 00:38:06,470
I can't simply practice any martial arts for no reason.

669
00:38:06,470 --> 00:38:07,780
If it can't cure the Gang Qi,

670
00:38:07,780 --> 00:38:08,760
and I'm obsessed because of it,

671
00:38:08,760 --> 00:38:09,650
it's not worth it.

672
00:38:09,650 --> 00:38:10,740
I won't practice it.

673
00:38:10,740 --> 00:38:11,110
No.

674
00:38:13,480 --> 00:38:15,130
Do you know why Di Feisheng

675
00:38:16,500 --> 00:38:17,830
wanted me to save lives?

676
00:38:19,210 --> 00:38:20,940
It's because of this skill set.

677
00:38:21,170 --> 00:38:22,370
If you don't trust me,

678
00:38:22,560 --> 00:38:24,000
or you doubt me, it's fine.

679
00:38:24,000 --> 00:38:25,530
But Di Feisheng's judgment

680
00:38:25,820 --> 00:38:26,800
can't be wrong.

681
00:38:29,580 --> 00:38:30,470
You don't want it?

682
00:38:30,470 --> 00:38:31,930
Fine, if you don't want it, give it to me.

683
00:38:31,930 --> 00:38:32,660
Give it to me.

684
00:38:35,540 --> 00:38:36,820
Listen, Fang Xiaobao,

685
00:38:37,090 --> 00:38:38,550
how can you be a detective?

686
00:38:38,750 --> 00:38:40,310
You're such a fool,

687
00:38:40,330 --> 00:38:40,860
an idiot.

688
00:38:40,870 --> 00:38:41,990
How can you be a detective?

689
00:38:41,990 --> 00:38:43,430
Can't you think about

690
00:38:43,540 --> 00:38:44,850
why Di Feisheng

691
00:38:45,010 --> 00:38:46,750
used you to threaten me to save others?

692
00:38:46,750 --> 00:38:49,350
If the Gang Qi in your body is getting more serious,

693
00:38:49,350 --> 00:38:50,990
you'll fall into his trap

694
00:38:51,620 --> 00:38:53,150
because you have to listen to him.

695
00:38:53,150 --> 00:38:54,480
What should you do then?

696
00:38:54,520 --> 00:38:56,000
That devil keeps killing people

697
00:38:56,000 --> 00:38:56,860
and keeps doing evil.

698
00:38:56,860 --> 00:38:58,120
Don't you feel guilty?

699
00:38:58,250 --> 00:38:59,510
-Do you want to practice it or not?
-Fine.

700
00:38:59,510 --> 00:39:00,180
I will practice it.

701
00:39:00,180 --> 00:39:01,050
You're talking too much.

702
00:39:01,050 --> 00:39:02,710
I won't let the devil succeed.

703
00:39:03,050 --> 00:39:03,960
Remember.

704
00:39:04,360 --> 00:39:05,200
If I

705
00:39:05,570 --> 00:39:07,010
go crazy,

706
00:39:07,030 --> 00:39:07,660
foam at the mouth

707
00:39:07,660 --> 00:39:09,060
and dance uncontrollably after practising it,

708
00:39:09,060 --> 00:39:11,270
do remember to find me a physician from the town.

709
00:39:11,270 --> 00:39:12,000
Don't worry.

710
00:39:12,610 --> 00:39:15,410
I'll get you any expensive medicine if you need it.

711
00:39:15,850 --> 00:39:16,710
Practice hard.

712
00:39:19,460 --> 00:39:20,300
Fine.

713
00:39:45,420 --> 00:39:46,660
After all, you've called Li Xiangyi

714
00:39:46,660 --> 00:39:48,320
your master for so many years.

715
00:39:48,690 --> 00:39:50,690
I'll pass this Yangzhouman to you.

716
00:39:51,890 --> 00:39:54,840
It's a way to repay his promise to you.

717
00:40:23,260 --> 00:40:24,320
What are you doing?

718
00:40:24,680 --> 00:40:26,280
Are you sleepwalking at night?

719
00:40:26,280 --> 00:40:26,940
Li Lianhua,

720
00:40:27,660 --> 00:40:29,460
where did you get that skill set?

721
00:40:29,580 --> 00:40:30,580
Didn't I tell you?

722
00:40:30,620 --> 00:40:31,500
It's ancestral.

723
00:40:31,500 --> 00:40:32,230
Impossible.

724
00:40:33,210 --> 00:40:34,560
The skill set is profound and mysterious.

725
00:40:34,560 --> 00:40:35,560
It's very useful.

726
00:40:35,780 --> 00:40:37,580
Even Tianji Hall's Mind-reading Skills

727
00:40:37,580 --> 00:40:38,710
can't compare to it.

728
00:40:39,370 --> 00:40:40,830
If it's really ancestral,

729
00:40:41,150 --> 00:40:44,540
there must have been many high-skilled warriors coming from your family.

730
00:40:44,540 --> 00:40:45,100
Tell me.

731
00:40:45,700 --> 00:40:46,830
Where did you get it?

732
00:40:47,590 --> 00:40:48,590
Let go of me!

733
00:40:49,200 --> 00:40:49,860
No manners.

734
00:40:52,670 --> 00:40:53,050
Fine.

735
00:40:54,220 --> 00:40:56,950
One year, I went to the mountain to collect herbs.

736
00:40:57,340 --> 00:40:59,400
Unfortunately, I fell off the cliff.

737
00:40:59,820 --> 00:41:01,890
Suddenly, in front of a cave,

738
00:41:01,960 --> 00:41:03,720
a fairy godmother appeared.

739
00:41:04,050 --> 00:41:05,980
She asked me to kowtow thrice to her

740
00:41:06,430 --> 00:41:08,240
and passed me the set of skills.

741
00:41:08,890 --> 00:41:10,410
After thinking about it,

742
00:41:10,820 --> 00:41:13,820
I realised that was a legendary immortal fate.

743
00:41:14,930 --> 00:41:15,430
Bah!

744
00:41:16,250 --> 00:41:18,380
How can there be like the pie in the sky?

745
00:41:18,380 --> 00:41:19,280
Didn't I tell you?

746
00:41:19,280 --> 00:41:20,410
It's all fate.

747
00:41:20,830 --> 00:41:21,550
Tell me

748
00:41:22,040 --> 00:41:23,840
what the name of the skill set is.

749
00:41:24,260 --> 00:41:25,190
That's amazing.

750
00:41:26,010 --> 00:41:27,590
It's almost the same as Yangzhouman.

751
00:41:27,590 --> 00:41:28,590
It's Suzhoukuai.

752
00:41:29,730 --> 00:41:30,860
I'm not buying that.

753
00:41:32,200 --> 00:41:33,480
You know what?

754
00:41:33,610 --> 00:41:35,460
You asked me to tell you, but you don't believe me after I told you.

755
00:41:35,460 --> 00:41:36,620
Then explain to me

756
00:41:37,230 --> 00:41:39,080
why I, a physician who sells plasters,

757
00:41:39,080 --> 00:41:40,860
can get the ultimate skill set.

758
00:41:46,380 --> 00:41:48,380
If I were born good at martial arts,

759
00:41:48,710 --> 00:41:50,170
I would have become a hero.

760
00:41:51,300 --> 00:41:52,230
Unfortunately,

761
00:41:52,380 --> 00:41:53,780
we have different fates.

762
00:41:54,130 --> 00:41:56,130
I can only be a wandering physician.

763
00:41:56,580 --> 00:41:57,540
Unlike someone,

764
00:41:58,080 --> 00:41:59,810
who's going to be a master soon.

765
00:42:00,870 --> 00:42:01,480
All right.

766
00:42:01,960 --> 00:42:04,010
I owe you this time.

767
00:42:06,770 --> 00:42:08,680
It's okay if you don't know martial arts.

768
00:42:08,680 --> 00:42:09,880
It's the same if I can.

769
00:42:10,510 --> 00:42:12,580
After we get out of here, I'll take care of you

770
00:42:12,580 --> 00:42:13,500
and protect you.

771
00:42:13,500 --> 00:42:15,250
No matter what happens, just mention my name.

772
00:42:15,250 --> 00:42:16,310
Most importantly,

773
00:42:17,500 --> 00:42:19,110
I kowtowed three times

774
00:42:19,580 --> 00:42:20,710
to get the skill set.

775
00:42:20,930 --> 00:42:22,900
So you also have to kowtow thrice to me

776
00:42:22,900 --> 00:42:24,430
so that I can feel better.

777
00:42:26,490 --> 00:42:27,280
Dream on.

778
00:42:27,640 --> 00:42:28,540
Except for my parents,

779
00:42:28,540 --> 00:42:30,390
I'll only kowtow to my master, Li Xiangyi.

780
00:42:30,390 --> 00:42:31,150
Who are you?

781
00:42:31,540 --> 00:42:32,580
Your Suzhoukuai

782
00:42:32,900 --> 00:42:35,900
is definitely not as good as my master's Yangzhouman.

783
00:42:36,380 --> 00:42:37,270
Take your time.

784
00:42:37,840 --> 00:42:38,500
Li Lianhua,

785
00:42:38,760 --> 00:42:39,470
why don't you tell me more

786
00:42:39,470 --> 00:42:40,470
about my master?

787
00:42:40,630 --> 00:42:41,580
You said too little last time.

788
00:42:41,580 --> 00:42:42,460
I haven't heard enough yet.

789
00:42:42,460 --> 00:42:43,950
Don't you feel hot

790
00:42:43,980 --> 00:42:45,180
and chest tightness?

791
00:42:45,850 --> 00:42:46,310
No.

792
00:42:46,530 --> 00:42:48,930
The crucial part of Suzhoukuai is silence.

793
00:42:49,620 --> 00:42:50,950
Most importantly, talk less

794
00:42:50,950 --> 00:42:51,680
and be quiet.

795
00:42:51,740 --> 00:42:53,440
When you talk, you'll spend your energy and cause blood flow.

796
00:42:53,440 --> 00:42:55,170
It'll boom like a firecracker.

797
00:42:55,230 --> 00:42:56,270
It's up to you.

